---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="About MegaBite | Restaurant Technology Experts" 
  description="MegaBite is a vendor-agnostic restaurant technology consulting firm specializing in POS integration, online ordering, and digital transformation. Serving Denver, Boulder, and restaurants nationwide."
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-50 to-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
          <div class="inline-block bg-primary-100 text-primary-700 px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold mb-4">
            Denver & Boulder, Colorado
          </div>
          <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-600 to-primary-500 bg-clip-text text-transparent leading-tight">
            The Only Vendor-Agnostic Technology Partner for Independent Restaurants
          </h1>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 mb-6">
            We don't sell POS systems. We don't take vendor kickbacks. We architect the right solution, 
            integrate it, and manage it—100% aligned with your success.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-100 to-primary-50 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-primary-200">
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="w-32 h-32 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-500 to-primary-600 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-5xl text-white font-bold">MB</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Your Fractional CTO</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Restaurant Technology Expert</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Story -->
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">The Market Problem We Solve</h2>
      
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-700 space-y-6">
        <p>
          The Denver and Boulder restaurant technology market is broken. It's fragmented into two groups: 
          <strong>generalist consultants who identify problems but don't implement solutions</strong>, and 
          <strong>POS resellers who push biased, single-brand products because they're commissioned salespeople</strong>.
        </p>

        <p>
          Independent operators are trapped navigating this alone. They hire a consultant who tells them their 
          food costs are high. They find an inventory system, but it needs POS integration. They call a reseller 
          who only sells their brand. Meanwhile, their systems don't talk to each other, and nobody is managing 
          the whole stack.
        </p>

        <p>
          <strong>Megabite fills the uncontested gap:</strong> We're the first vendor-agnostic integrator and 
          fractional CTO for independent restaurants. We architect your complete tech stack (POS, inventory, 
          labor, CRM) from best-in-class tools, integrate it into a unified platform, implement it with 
          comprehensive staff training, and manage it ongoing as your data analyst and technology partner.
        </p>

        <p class="text-primary-700 font-semibold italic">
          We succeed when you succeed. No vendor kickbacks. No sales quotas. Just expert guidance 
          100% aligned with your profitability.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Approach -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-50 to-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center text-gray-900 mb-4">How We're Different</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 text-center mb-16 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Unlike consultants, resellers, or IT providers, we solve the complete problem
      </p>
      
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-primary-100">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary-500 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">We Implement, Not Just Recommend</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">
            Unlike Gilkey or RCSI, we don't just deliver a report. We architect the solution, 
            configure the systems, and train your staff.
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-primary-600 font-semibold">
            vs. General Consultants
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-primary-100">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary-500 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">We're Vendor-Agnostic, Not Biased</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">
            Unlike RDS or EMS, we don't push one brand. Toast is great for some, Square for others, 
            Lightspeed for fine dining. We recommend what's right for <em>you</em>.
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-primary-600 font-semibold">
            vs. POS Resellers
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-primary-100">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary-500 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">We're Restaurant Ops, Not Just IT</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">
            Unlike Greystone Tech, we don't just manage your network. We understand menu engineering, 
            labor scheduling, and inventory costing—because that's where the ROI lives.
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-primary-600 font-semibold">
            vs. IT/MSP Providers
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Let's Talk About Your Restaurant</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-12">
        Schedule a free 30-minute consultation to discuss how technology can help your business.
      </p>
      <a 
        href="/#schedule" 
        class="inline-block bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-500 to-primary-600 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full text-lg font-semibold hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105"
      >
        Book Free Consultation
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
